definition: Liaoyuan prefecture-level city in Jilin province 吉林省 in northeast China
short name for Liaoning 遼寧|辽宁[Liao2 ning2] province/Liao or Khitan dynasty (907-1125)

sentences.english: It recently conducted surprise inspections in Liaoyuan, a city in Jilin Province, the newspaper reported.
sentences.chinese: 最近對吉林省遼源市進行了突擊檢查。
